# todo.md — active to-dos

> The owner's actual action items. Auto-loaded every session (Tier 1) — the agent
> surfaces items due today/tomorrow at session start and ignores stale ones. Completed
> items move to an archive.
>
> 실제 할 일 목록. 매 세션 자동 로드 — 에이전트는 오늘/내일 기한 항목만 세션 시작 시 알림.

## TODO vs. calendar

| Put here (TODO) | Put on the calendar |
|---|---|
| decisions, tasks, things to send, follow-ups — anything requiring **active** action | attendance, appointments — **passive** time-blocks |

The calendar's dates are truth. Don't re-derive or second-guess them here.

